results.deck: A publishing company based in the city of Berlin, Germany, founded in 2005
results.description: By now, the company focusses primarily on the MMO genre, and have published titles such as Runes of Magic and Chronicles of Spellborn in Europe. The CEO of the company is Christoph Gerlinger, a veteran in the gaming industry. Frogster was founded in 2005 and aquired all the assets of German publisher Pointsoft Company (founded in 1999). The company has been releasing games under the following sub-brands, ANACONDA, Back to Games, Brigades, Eclypse and Hall of Fame.
